+.Sh NAME
+.Nm efisecdb
+.Nd utility for managing UEFI signature lists
+.Sh SYNOPSIS
+.Nm
+.Bk -words
+.Oo Fl s Ar SORT Oc
+.Oo Fl i Ar file Oo Fl i Ar file
+.Oc ... Oc
+\ \p
