+00000030  d1 2e 99 4b 6d 48 5d 2c  71 67 72 8a a5 52 59 84  |...KmH],qgr..RY.|
+00000040  ad 5c a6 1e 75 16 22 1f  07 9a 14 36              |.\..u."....6|
